1980;;...Maybe This Time;;Australian;;Chris McGill;;Judy Morris, Bill Hunter, Michael Preston, Michele Fawdon, Leonard Teale, Chris Haywood, Rod Mullinar;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maybe_This_Time_(1980_film);;Fran, the assistant to university professor Paddy, is about to turn 30. She is having an affair with a married minister's aide, Stephen. She returns home to the country town she grew up in and has a fling with an old flame, Alan. She also begins sleeping with Paddy.